bitbit
======
A bitboard based chess engine written in c.


Building bitbit
---------------
Run

	make

in the root directory. To choose a transposition table size, run

	make TT={size}

size is by default specified in bytes. For a 128 MiB transposition
table, run

	make TT=128M

K and G are also valid suffixes. The default size is 64 MiB.
